/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: RolePermission */
/*==============================================================*/
create table RolePermission (
RolePermissionId int not null,
RoleId int not null,
PermissionId int not null,
Enable bit not null,
CreationDate datetime not null,
constraint PK_ROLEPERMISSION primary key (RolePermissionId)
)
go

alter table RolePermission
add constraint FK_ROLEPERM_REFERENCE_ROLES foreign key (RoleId)
references Roles (RoleId)
go

alter table RolePermission
add constraint FK_ROLEPERM_REFERENCE_PERMISSI foreign key (PermissionId)
references Permissions (PermissionId)
go
